title: Bobby's Dog Rushed To ER + Favorite Songs From Movies Draft + Lunchbox Tries To Get Free Hotel Rooms
itunes:title: Bobby's Dog Rushed To ER + Favorite Songs From Movies Draft + Lunchbox Tries To Get Free Hotel Rooms
description:
Bobby talks about his eventful weekend at the vet after his dog Stanley ate some grapes...which they're not supposed to eat. He gives a PSA on foods that are harmful to dogs. We draft our favorite songs from movies. Plus, Lunchbox calls hotels rooms in Vegas to try and get free rooms for Raymundo’s bachelor party this month!
